patterns:\n+      - pattern: lock($X) { ... }\n+    message: |\n+      CRITICAL: lock() is BANNED in V12 DNA. Use Interlocked operations or Actor model.\n+      Legacy lock(stateLock) violates the Lock-Free Kernel mandate.\n+      \n+      Fix: Replace with Interlocked.CompareExchange or FSM/Actor Enqueue pattern.\n+      See: docs/architecture.md for Actor pattern examples.\n+    languages: [csharp]\n+    severity: ERROR\n+    metadata:\n+      category: security\n+      cwe: \"CWE-667: Improper Locking\"\n+      confidence: HIGH\n+      v12_dna: lock-free-kernel\n+      priority: P0\n+      likelihood: HIGH\n+      impact: HIGH\n+      subcategory:\n+        - vuln\n+      \n+  - id: v12-atomic-on-local-variable\n+    patterns:\n+      - pattern: |\n+          var $LOCAL = ...;\n+          ...\n+          Interlocked.CompareExchange(ref $LOCAL, ...)\n+      - pattern: |\n+          var $LOCAL = ...;\n+          ...\n+          Interlocked.Exchange(ref $LOCAL, ...)\n+    message: |\n+      CRITICAL: Interlocked operation on local variable is non-atomic.\n+      Must operate on shared state (class field) for thread safety.\n+      \n+      Fix: Move variable to class scope or use different synchronization.\n+    languages: [csharp]\n+    severity: ERROR\n+    metadata:\n+      category: security\n+      cwe: \"CWE-362: Concurrent Execution using Shared Resource with Improper Synchronization\"\n+      confidence: HIGH\n+      v12_dna: atomic-unification\n+      priority: P0\n+      likelihood: HIGH\n+      impact: HIGH\n+      subcategory:\n+        - vuln\n+\n+  - id: v12-unicode-in-string-literals\n+    patterns:\n+      - pattern-regex: '[\"''].*[^\\x00-\\x7F].*[\"'']'\n+    message: |\n+      CRITICAL: Unicode/emoji detected in string literal. V12 DNA mandates ASCII-only.\n+      \n+      Common substitutions:\n+      - (!) instead of Г”ГңГЎВҙВ©Г…\n+      - -- instead of Г”ГҮГ¶\n+      - -> instead of Г”ГҘГҶ\n+      - Use straight quotes \"\" not curly \"\"\n+   